# Backend TDD Test Plan

## Context

Backend has 10 controllers, 8 services, 16 repositories, 4 validators, utilities. Existing tests cover controller layer (mocking services) + BDD acceptance scenarios. **Gap**: service business logic, validators, utilities, repositories, integration — all untested. Goal: comprehensive TDD coverage bottom-up.

## Test Architecture

```
Layer 0: Validators + Utilities     (pure logic, no deps)
Layer 1: Service unit tests         (mock IUnitOfWork + repos)
Layer 2: Repository + DbContext     (EF InMemory or SQLite)
Layer 3: Integration tests          (WebApplicationFactory)
Layer 4: Middleware                  (custom pipeline tests)
```

