## Summary

| Phase | Tests | Priority |
|-------|-------|----------|
| 1. Validators | ~20 | HIGH — pure logic, fast |
| 2. Utilities | ~33 | HIGH — pure logic, fast (incl. Result, TmdbMapping, CsvEscape) |
| 3. Services | ~90 | CRITICAL — business logic |
| 4. External (TMDB) | ~6 | MEDIUM |
| 5. Middleware | ~4 | LOW |
| 6. DbContext + Repo | ~15 | MEDIUM — needs InMemory provider |
| 7. Integration | ~10 | LOW — stretch goal |
| **Total** | **~178** | |

## Verification

After each phase:
1. `dotnet test --filter "FullyQualifiedName~TrackListTests.Validators"` (etc.)
2. `dotnet test --collect:"XPlat Code Coverage"` for coverage report
3. All existing tests must still pass (regression check)

